Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:53.06,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}どうすれば この心は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:59.58,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}鏡に映るの
